《'''我們的日子'''》（{{lang-en|''Days of Our Lives''}}，簡稱{{lang|en|''Days''}}或{{lang|en|''DOOL''}}）為美國的[[全國廣播公司|NBC]]電視台製播的一部日間[[肥皂劇|肥皂劇]]，也是世界上少數仍在在播的長壽電視劇，從1965年11月8日開始每星期播5集，<ref name="startdate">{{cite news|title=Cinema|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,901746,00.html|work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]|accessdate=2007-06-10|date=1965-11-05|archive-date=2007-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930095300/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,901746,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在不少國家也播放過。<ref name="australia">{{cite news|title=A new day for Nine|url=http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2004/08/26/1093456731202.html|publisher=[[The_Age|The Age]]|accessdate=2007-06-10|location=Melbourne|date=2004-08-26|archive-date=2012-04-18|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/670xorYON?url=http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2004/08/26/1093456731202.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="daysnz">{{cite web|title=TVNZ Schedules|url=http://tvnz.co.nz/days-of-our-lives|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090525073503/http://tvnz.co.nz/days-of-our-lives|archivedate=2009-05-25|publisher=[[TVNZ|TVNZ]]|accessdate=2007-06-10|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="daysuk">{{cite web|title=''Days'' Yanked in UK|url=http://www.soapcentral.com/days/news/2001/0423-daysuk.php|publisher=Soap Central|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-date=2016-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202060000/http://soapcentral.com/days/news/2001/0423-daysuk.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>到目前為止{{When}}重播時段依然維持當初肥皂劇播出的時段：上午七點，而首播時間則是在晚間8點或12點(東區/西區)。這部戲是由知名夫妻團隊[[Ted_Corday|Ted Corday]][[Betty_Corday|Betty Corday]]創作。<ref name="creators">{{cite web|url=http://www.etonline.com/news/83715_Days_of_our_Lives_Matriarch_Frances_Reid_Has_Died/|title='Days of our Lives' Matriarch Frances Reid Has Died|date=2010-02-04|accessdate=2011-02-12|publisher=ET|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110710203443/http://www.etonline.com/news/83715_Days_of_our_Lives_Matriarch_Frances_Reid_Has_Died/|archivedate=2011-07-10}}</ref>[[Irna_Phillips|Irna Phillips]]是本劇的編劇，而[[William_J._Bell|William J. Bell]]則是早期的編劇。本劇已經重新續約至2014年。

由於本劇的成功，從1975年4月21日開始從原本30分鐘加長至60分鐘。而自從更改時間後，節目播出一半的「稍後回來下半段的『我們的日子』」則是請知名男演員[[Macdonald_Carey|Macdonald Carey]]獻聲。我們的日子是美國第二長的長壽劇（第一名是[[綜合醫院_(美國電視劇)|綜合醫院]]），同時也是世界上現存繼續播放的第四長的長壽劇。

本劇主要描述兩個家庭：荷頓(Hortons)家族和布雷迪(Bradys)家族。<ref name="Days of our Lives Summary">{{cite web|url=http://www.tv.com/shows/days-of-our-lives/|title=Days Summary|accessdate=2007-06-10|publisher=TV.com|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226124421/http://www.tv.com/shows/days-of-our-lives/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 很多其他家族也進入到這個團隊，並且偶爾露面。荷頓家族的女家長，[[Frances_Reid|Frances Reid]]從該劇成立以來一直參與演出直到2010年2月3日逝世。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.soapoperadigest.com/soapstarstats/francesreidbio/index.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050320062408/http://soapoperadigest.com/soapstarstats/francesreidbio/index.html|archivedate=2005-03-20|title=Frances Reid — Days of our Lives — Bio — DAYS — ALice|publisher=Soapoperadigest.com|date=|accessdate=2010-05-25|deadurl=yes}}</ref>[[Suzanne_Rogers|Suzanne Rogers]]在我們的日子38周年慶生會中，回顧她於1973年第一次出場。<ref name="The Suzanne Rogers Interview">{{cite web|url=http://daysblips.dailyradar.com/story/the-suzanne-rogers-interview-part-one/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091024162159/http://daysblips.dailyradar.com/story/the-suzanne-rogers-interview-part-one/|archivedate=2009-10-24|title=The Suzanne Rogers Interview|publisher=Daily Radar.com|deadurl=yes}}</ref>Susan Seaforth Hayes則是唯一的從開播到現在都還在的角色。<ref name="Susan Seaforth Hayes">{{cite web|url=http://www.soapoperadigest.com/soapstarstats/susanseaforthhayesbio/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090215043134/http://soapoperadigest.com/soapstarstats/susanseaforthhayesbio/|archivedate=2009-02-15|title=Susan Seaforth Hayes Bio|publisher=Soap Opera Digest.com|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

'''我們的日子'''於2005年2月21日播出第10000集。<ref name="Days of our Lives Season 40, Ep # 10,000">{{cite web|url=http://www.ovguide.com/tv_episode/days-of-our-lives-season-40-episode-74-ep-10000-5536|title=Days of our Lives Season 40, Ep # 10,000|publisher=OVGuide.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120317061907/http://www.ovguide.com/tv_episode/days-of-our-lives-season-40-episode-74-ep-10000-5536|archivedate=2012-03-17}}</ref><ref name="Days of our Lives Celebration">{{cite web|url=http://www.soapoperadigest.com/features/days-of-our-lives/features/dayscelebration/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100209085051/http://www.soapoperadigest.com/features/days-of-our-lives/features/dayscelebration/|archivedate=2010-02-09|title=Days of our Lives Celebration|publisher=Soap Opera Digest.com|deadurl=yes}}</ref>本劇在1970年代被封為最大膽的戲劇，因為其他肥皂劇做不出類似的主題。<ref name="timerate">{{cite news|title=TIME Rates the Soaps|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,913849,00.html|publisher=[[TIME|TIME]]|accessdate=2007-06-09|date=1976-01-12|archive-date=2013-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814020430/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,913849,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>本劇的執行製作是[[Ken_Corday|Ken Corday]]，<ref name="Soap Opera Digest' 1998, page 42">''Soap Opera Digest'' article, issue of February 10, 1998, page 42</ref>聯合執行製作人則是[[Gary_Tomlin|Gary Tomlin]]。'''我們的日子'''是美國最知名的肥皂劇。<ref name="Josef Adalian">{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117966619?refCatId=14|title=iTunes plays ''Days''|date=2007-06-10|accessdate=2007-06-10|author=Josef Adalian|publisher=''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]''|archive-date=2012-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121225111417/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117966619/?refCatId=14|dead-url=no}}</ref> 原始的標題也是由知名演員[[MacDonald_Carey|MacDonald Carey]]所朗誦，也是使用至今。本劇也曾被知名情境喜劇[[六人行|六人行]]惡搞過，一些演員也跨至六人行客串，包括[[Kristian_Alfonso|Kristian Alfonso]]、<ref name="ramoray6">{{cite web|title=''Friends'': The One That Could Have Been, Part I|url=http://www.tv.com/shows/friends/the-one-with-joeys-award-34225/|publisher=[[TV.com|TV.com]]|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226005633/http://www.tv.com/shows/friends/the-one-with-joeys-award-34225/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Roark_Critchlow|Roark Critchlow]]、<ref name="ramoray7">{{cite web|title=''Friends'': The One After the Super Bowl|url=http://www.tv.com/shows/friends/the-one-after-the-super-bowl-1-380/|publisher=[[TV.com|TV.com]]|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108073458/http://www.tv.com/shows/friends/the-one-after-the-super-bowl-1-380/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Matthew_Ashford|Matthew Ashford]]、[[Kyle_Lowder|Kyle Lowder]]和[[Alison_Sweeney|Alison Sweeney]]等人。<ref name="ramoray5">{{cite web|title=''Friends'': The One With Joey's Award|url=http://www.tv.com/shows/friends/the-one-that-could-have-been-1-480/|publisher=[[TV.com|TV.com]]|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-date=2021-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224172416/http://www.tv.com/shows/friends/the-one-that-could-have-been-1-480/|dead-url=no}}</ref>本劇擁有大批知名粉絲諸如[[茱莉亞·羅勃茲|茱莉亞·羅勃茲]],<ref name="julia">{{cite web|title=Daytime's Secret Weapon|last=Fonseca|first=Nicholas|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,640535_1,00.html|publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|accessdate=2007-06-08|archive-date=2007-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012210348/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C640535_1%2C00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>已故的前[[美國最高法院|美國最高法院]]大法官[[Thurgood_Marshall|Thurgood Marshall]]。<ref name="marshall">{{cite news|title=Sex and Suffering in the Afternoon|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,913850-1,00.html|publisher=[[TIME|TIME]]|accessdate=2007-06-08|date=1976-01-12|archive-date=2013-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522071516/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,913850-1,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
Cordays夫妻和Bell結合傳統醫院肥皂劇的概念創造一個新的影集描述一個家庭。這個概念包含傳統的家庭劇，而這個家庭都是醫生，包括一個成員在大醫院工作。<ref>Gilbert, Annie, ''All My Afternoons'', p. 110.</ref>故事大綱就是一個在美國中部的[[沙隆鎮|沙隆鎮]](Salem)裡有一個中上層社會的家庭，包含傳統的親子關係，結婚，離婚和家庭生活，再加上一些跟醫生這個職業發生的故事還有心理上個人的性格問題等。<ref>Gilbert, Annie, ''All My Afternoons'', p. 111.</ref>最早的執行製作是[[Al_Rabin|Al Rabin]]對於角色熱情相當自豪，曾說過這些角色並不害怕「分享他們的問題」。<ref name="alrabin">{{cite news|title=Move Over, Sam Ervin|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,964312,00.html|publisher=[[TIME|TIME]]|accessdate=2007-06-09|date=1987-05-11|first=Walter|last=Shapiro|archive-date=2013-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130819185521/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,964312,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

當初的評論認為這個影集並不依賴懷舊而受到好評，並認為寫實地描述一個美國當代家庭。<ref name="Gilbert, Annie p. 109">Gilbert, Annie, ''All My Afternoons'', p. 109</ref>到了1970年代，評論者認為「我們的日子」是相當大膽的日間戲劇，引領當時的其他戲劇所不敢接觸的主題，例如:[[人工授精|人工授精]]和不同種族間的戀愛。<ref name="timerate"/>1976年1月12日，「我們的日子」的演員[[Bill_Hayes_(actor)|Bill Hayes]] and [[Susan_Seaforth_Hayes|Susan Seaforth Hayes]]登上了[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]的封面。這是第一次有日間連續劇的演員登上該雜誌的封面。<ref name="SOD stats Seaforth">{{cite web|url=http://www.soapoperadigest.com/soapstarstats/susanseaforthhayesbio/|title=Soap Star Stats: Susan Seaforth Hayes (Julie, ''DAYS'')|publisher=SoapOperaDigest.com|accessdate=May 20, 2009|archive-date=2010-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100123212146/http://www.soapoperadigest.com/soapstarstats/susanseaforthhayesbio/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="1985 Encyc">{{cite book |last=Schemering |first=Christopher |authorlink=Christopher Schemering |title=''[[The_Soap_Opera_Encyclopedia|The Soap Opera Encyclopedia]]'' |pages=[https://archive.org/details/soapoperaencyclo0000sche_z6n5/page/66 66]–73 |isbn=0-345-32459-5 |date=September 1985}}</ref><ref name="Time 1976">{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,913850,00.html|title=Sex and Suffering in the Afternoon|date=January 12, 1976|work=''[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]''|publisher=Time.com|accessdate=May 20, 2009|archive-date=2005-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050113135820/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,913850,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>Hayeses夫妻在現實生活中也成為夫妻(他們在1970年因戲劇認識而在1974年結婚)。這對夫妻在當時大量出現在各大肥皂劇雜誌封面還有各式媒體。<ref name="1997 Encyc">{{cite book|last=Waggett|first=Gerard J.|title=''The Soap Opera Encyclopedia''|url=https://archive.org/details/soapoperaencyclo00wagg|publisher=[[Harper_Paperbacks|Harper Paperbacks]]|date=November 1997|page=[https://archive.org/details/soapoperaencyclo00wagg/page/91 91]|chapter=''One Life to Live''|isbn=0-06-101157-6}}</ref>

時間來到1990年代，本劇跨足到超自然的劇情，評論也開始關心，因為似乎本劇開始背離原先的故事設定。然而，這些新的劇情還是有新的效果出現，使得「我」劇成為日間肥皂劇中的收視冠軍，收視群包括中年婦女和年輕人。也成為最賺錢的一部影集之一。<ref name = "marlenadevil"/><ref name="supernatural">{{cite news|title=Love, Money, Witches and Beach Grass|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,991471,00.html|publisher=[[TIME|TIME]]|accessdate=2007-06-09|date=1999-07-12|archive-date=2013-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130825044014/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,991471,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 在2006年，扮演其中一個角色[[Jack_Deveraux|Jack Deveraux]]的男演員[[Matthew_Ashford|Matthew Ashford]]在被問到他的角色「死而復活」第三次時回應道：「這個角色對我來說越來越難演，是因為這個角色越來越奇怪...我會看劇本想『這是啥』這是『[[卡通頻道|卡通頻道]]』嗎？」<ref name="ashford">{{cite news|title=What you didn't see at the Daytime Emmys|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2006-05-01-daytime-emmys_x.htm|publisher=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|accessdate=2007-06-10|date=2006-05-01|archive-date=2009-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090521213335/http://www.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2006-05-01-daytime-emmys_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

「我」劇除了受到雜誌上的好評，也拿過不少獎項，包括[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]的最佳影片(1978年)。<ref name="emmy78">{{cite web|title=Daytime Emmys - 1977|url=http://www.soapcentral.com/soapcentral/awards/emmys/1977.php|publisher=Soap Central|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-date=2011-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629115850/http://www.soapcentral.com/soapcentral/awards/emmys/1977.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>還有編劇協會(東區)獎的最佳影片(2000年)。<ref name="wga">{{cite web|title=52nd Annual Writers Guild Awards|url=http://www.wgaeast.org/awards2000/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070430185254/http://www.wgaeast.org/awards2000/|archivedate=2007-04-30|publisher=[[Writers_Guild_of_America|Writers Guild of America]]|accessdate=2007-06-10|deadurl=yes}}</ref>「我」劇的演員也得過不少獎項：[[Macdonald_Carey|Macdonald Carey]] (湯姆何頓醫生)贏得最佳男演員(1974)。<ref name="emmy74">{{cite web|title=Daytime Emmys - 1973|url=http://www.soapcentral.com/soapcentral/awards/emmys/1973.php|publisher=Soap Central|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-date=2011-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629115900/http://www.soapcentral.com/soapcentral/awards/emmys/1973.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name = "emmy75"/> [[Susan_Flannery|Susan Flannery]](羅娜何頓)在1975年贏得最佳女演員。<ref name="emmy75">{{cite web|title=Daytime Emmys - 1974|url=http://www.soapcentral.com/soapcentral/awards/emmys/1974.php|publisher=Soap Central|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-date=2011-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629115908/http://www.soapcentral.com/soapcentral/awards/emmys/1974.php|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[Suzanne_Rogers|Suzanne Rogers]](麥姬何頓)，[[Leann_Hunley|Leann Hunley]]([[Anna_Fredericks|Anna DiMera]])，和[[Tamara_Braun|Tamara Braun]]([[Ava_Vitali|Ava Vitali]])等也贏過最佳女配角，分別在1979年，<ref name="emmy79">{{cite web|title=Daytime Emmys - 1978|url=http://www.soapcentral.com/soapcentral/awards/emmys/1978.php|publisher=Soap Central|accessdate=2007-06-10|archive-date=2011-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629115919/http://www.soapcentral.com/soapcentral/awards/emmys/